storemanagerforprestashop.author: PrestaShop Partners
storemanagerforprestashop.fullDescription:
30-DAY FREE TRIAL!  The back office solution you need to run your PrestaShop online store efficiently !
Store Manager for PrestaShop will save you over 2 hours a day by automating daily tasks and making it simple to update your shop.
 
Store Manager for PrestaShop is a desktop application, designed to speed up and automate the management of PrestaShop based stores. Not only does it take care of the mass operations with products, categories, orders and customers extending the functionality of the store web back-end, but also lines up with an intuitive interface and advanced addons for easy store management.
Save your time, money, and resources by allowing Store Manager for PrestaShop do all the job for you.
Store Manager for PrestaShop will make your store stand out from the crowd!
 
*** WINNER OF THE PRESTASHOP AWARDS CEREMONY FOR THE BEST MODULE ***
storemanagerforprestashop.additionalDescription:
Save your time, money, and resources by allowing Store Manager for PrestaShop do all the job for you.
Store Manager for PrestaShop will make your store stand out from the crowd!
 
Spend an Hour, Save a Day!
Store Manager for PrestaShop was designed to work for you and not at the expense of your business. It is your personal assistant that does all the routine tasks, saving you tons of time for greater deeds.
For that matter, it provides with ready-made export/import features, report tools, advanced addons, etc. No need to spend a day getting deep into how your store works, spend an hour understanding how Store Manager does the job for you.
 
Take Your Online Business to the Bank
Buy one Store Manager instead of multiple modules.
Use one Store Manager license to manage your multiple stores. Store Manager doesn’t require any special skills, so you don’t have to pay someone to keep your store database organized. You can implement all the necessary updates yourself with Store Manager for PrestaShop and get on to important tasks.

googleshopping.name: googleshopping
googleshopping.description: Google Shopping helps businesses like you tap into the power of customer intent to reach the right people with relevant products ads, when it matters the most
googleshopping.author: PrestaShop Partners
googleshopping.fullDescription:
Google Shopping helps businesses like you tap into the power of customer intent to reach the right people with relevant products ads, when it matters the most. 

With Google Shopping, increase your sales by at least 30% !
googleshopping.additionalDescription:
With Google Shopping, put your product images, price, and business name right in front of people searching on Google, no matter what device they're using.
Benefits:
  • Increase visits to your shop being displayed among the 100 billions monthly Google searches 
  • Minimize workload and go-to-market time: Use the product information you already have in PrestaShop without needing to create separate files to submit to Google
  • Data accuracy: Continuously import fresh data from your store on PrestaShop without any additional work
  • Improve conversion rate thanks to qualified Google trafic as well as your ranking in the search engine

lanavettepickup.name: lanavettepickup
lanavettepickup.displayName: la Navette Pickup: deliver your parcels in parcelshops
lanavettepickup.description: La Navette Pickup is a parcelshop to parcelshop delivery service developed by Pickup, filial of the Groupe La Poste, and France’s 1st parcelshop network
lanavettepickup.author: PrestaShop Partners
lanavettepickup.fullDescription:
La Navette Pickup is a parcelshop to parcelshop delivery service developed by Pickup, filial of the Groupe La Poste, and France’s 1st parcelshop network.
This module enables you to have your parcels delivered in parcelshops in 48H from France.
lanavettepickup.additionalDescription:
For your customers: 
·        Economical: starting from 4,35€ (excl. Tax)
·        Fast: 24/48h
·        Safe: the recipient has to present and ID and sign to pick up the parcel.
·        Tracking: track your parcel in real-time and the recipient is notified by SMS and email when upon delivery.
 
For you:
·        Integrate our solution in a few clicks, with the help of our technical team if necessary
·        A dynamic map of our Pickup parcelshops on your website
·        Return to sender included (in case of refusal or no show of the recipient)
·        A dedicated Customer Service
·        Non-binding and no minimum volume or period
